{
  "id": "ObjStorSmokeTest01",
  "name": "IfcPipeline: Object Storage Smoke Test",
  "active": false,
  "isArchived": false,
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Object-Storage Smoke Test\n\nExercises the full ifcpipeline stack through the custom `n8n-nodes-ifcpipeline` **0.7.0** package against the **MinIO-backed** api-gateway (`http://api-gateway`).\n\n**Prerequisites**\n1. Stack running (`docker compose up -d`) with `USE_OBJECT_STORAGE=true`.\n2. Create an **IFC Pipeline API** credential:\n   - Base URL: `http://api-gateway`\n   - API Key: value of `IFC_PIPELINE_API_KEY` on the stack (e.g. `pocsecret`)\n   Assign it to **every** IfcPipeline node below.\n3. Sample files `/examples/Building-Architecture.ifc` and `/examples/IDS-example.ids` must be present inside the n8n container (they are by default — mounted from `./shared/examples`).\n\n**Flow**\n`Manual Trigger` → upload IFC & IDS to the bucket → fan out to **IfcCsv export**, **IfcTester** validation and **IfcToJson** → merge the three job results.\n\nEach worker returns `{ output_key, output_path: s3://… }` so you can confirm the artefacts landed in MinIO (`http://localhost:9001`, user `minioadmin` / `minioadmin`).",
        "width": 640,
        "height": 360,
        "color": 5
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-80, -460],
      "id": "sticky-smoke-readme",
      "name": "Readme"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-80, 40],
      "id": "node-trigger",
      "name": "When clicking 'Test workflow'"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "fileSelector": "/examples/Building-Architecture.ifc",
        "options": {
          "dataPropertyName": "data"
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.readWriteFile",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [180, -80],
      "id": "node-read-ifc",
      "name": "Read sample IFC"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "fileSelector": "/examples/IDS-example.ids",
        "options": {
          "dataPropertyName": "data"
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.readWriteFile",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [180, 160],
      "id": "node-read-ids",
      "name": "Read sample IDS"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "uploadFile",
        "fileType": "ifc",
        "binaryPropertyName": "data"
      },
      "type": "CUSTOM.ifcPipeline",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [440, -80],
      "id": "node-upload-ifc",
      "name": "Upload IFC → MinIO",
      "credentials": {
        "ifcPipelineApi": {
          "id": "__SET_ME__",
          "name": "IFC Pipeline API"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "uploadFile",
        "fileType": "ids",
        "binaryPropertyName": "data"
      },
      "type": "CUSTOM.ifcPipeline",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [440, 160],
      "id": "node-upload-ids",
      "name": "Upload IDS → MinIO",
      "credentials": {
        "ifcPipelineApi": {
          "id": "__SET_ME__",
          "name": "IFC Pipeline API"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "combine",
        "combineBy": "combineByPosition",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.merge",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [700, 40],
      "id": "node-merge-uploads",
      "name": "Merge uploaded keys"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "a1",
              "name": "ifc_key",
              "value": "={{ $('Upload IFC → MinIO').item.json.storage_ref || $('Upload IFC → MinIO').item.json.object_key }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "a2",
              "name": "ids_key",
              "value": "={{ $('Upload IDS → MinIO').item.json.storage_ref || $('Upload IDS → MinIO').item.json.object_key }}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [940, 40],
      "id": "node-set-refs",
      "name": "Pick storage refs"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "exportToCsv",
        "filename": "={{ $json.ifc_key }}",
        "outputFilename": "output/csv/Building-Architecture_export.csv",
        "options": {
          "format": "csv",
          "attributes": "Name,Description,GlobalId",
          "query": "IfcWall"
        },
        "waitForCompletion": true,
        "pollingInterval": 2,
        "timeout": 300
      },
      "type": "CUSTOM.ifcCsv",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1220, -140],
      "id": "node-ifccsv",
      "name": "IfcCsv: walls → CSV",
      "credentials": {
        "ifcPipelineApi": {
          "id": "__SET_ME__",
          "name": "IFC Pipeline API"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "validateIfc",
        "ifcFilename": "={{ $json.ifc_key }}",
        "idsFilename": "={{ $json.ids_key }}",
        "outputFilename": "output/ids/validation_report.json",
        "reportType": "json",
        "waitForCompletion": true,
        "pollingInterval": 2,
        "timeout": 300
      },
      "type": "CUSTOM.ifcTester",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1220, 40],
      "id": "node-ifctester",
      "name": "IfcTester: validate",
      "credentials": {
        "ifcPipelineApi": {
          "id": "__SET_ME__",
          "name": "IFC Pipeline API"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "convertToJson",
        "filename": "={{ $json.ifc_key }}",
        "outputFilename": "output/json/Building-Architecture.json",
        "waitForCompletion": true,
        "pollingInterval": 2,
        "timeout": 300
      },
      "type": "CUSTOM.ifcToJson",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1220, 220],
      "id": "node-ifc2json",
      "name": "IfcToJson: to JSON",
      "credentials": {
        "ifcPipelineApi": {
          "id": "__SET_ME__",
          "name": "IFC Pipeline API"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "combine",
        "combineBy": "combineAll",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.merge",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [1520, 40],
      "id": "node-merge-results",
      "name": "All results"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "r1",
              "name": "ifccsv_output_path",
              "value": "={{ $('IfcCsv: walls → CSV').item.json.result.output_path }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "r2",
              "name": "ifctester_output_path",
              "value": "={{ $('IfcTester: validate').item.json.result.output_path }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "r3",
              "name": "ifc2json_output_path",
              "value": "={{ $('IfcToJson: to JSON').item.json.result.output_path }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "r4",
              "name": "storage",
              "value": "={{ $('IfcCsv: walls → CSV').item.json.result.storage }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "r5",
              "name": "bucket",
              "value": "={{ $('IfcCsv: walls → CSV').item.json.result.bucket }}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [1760, 40],
      "id": "node-summary",
      "name": "Smoke-test summary"
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "When clicking 'Test workflow'": {
      "main": [
        [
          {"node": "Read sample IFC", "type": "main", "index": 0},
          {"node": "Read sample IDS", "type": "main", "index": 0}
